<isis lang="en">
    <stitle>VT 365 Diesel Engine - 2004 Model Year - ELECTRONICALLY CONTROLLED VARIABLE GEOMETRY TURBOCHARGER (VGT) -
        Installation - Control Valve (If previously removed)
    </stitle>
    <svcman/>
    <svcproc id="s26502.4.2" graphiccount="4">
        <title>Control Valve (If previously removed)</title>
        <figure id="f2650233" figsize="col-wide">
            <graphic filename="../figd15/d1507.webp" type="webp" scalefit="1" scalefitwidth="248px" box="no"/>
            <caption>O-ring lubrication</caption>
        </figure>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">During reassembly, lubricate new O-rings with clean engine oil. Make sure O-rings are seated
                correctly - not twisted or distorted.
            </para>
        </step1>
        <figure id="f2650234" figsize="col-wide">
            <graphic filename="../figd15/d1506.webp" type="webp" scalefit="1" scalefitwidth="248px" box="no"/>
            <caption>VGT control valve</caption>
        </figure>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Install control valve carefully to avoid twisting or cutting O-rings.</para>
        </step1>
        <specpara>
            <note>
                <para>Do not use the retaining bolt to draw the control valve into the housing. Push the VGT control
                    valve in by hand to seat securely before installing bracket and bolt.
                </para>
            </note>
        </specpara>
        <figure id="f2650235" figsize="col-wide">
            <graphic filename="../figD09/D09126.webp" type="webp" scalefit="1" scalefitwidth="248px" box="no"/>
            <caption>Retaining bolt for VGT Control valve</caption>
            <calloutgroup>
                <callout1 type="arabic">VGT control valve bracket</callout1>
                <callout1 type="arabic">Retaining bolt</callout1>
            </calloutgroup>
        </figure>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Install control valve bracket and retaining bolt and tighten bolt to standard torque .
            </para>
        </step1>
        <figure id="f2650236" figsize="col-wide">
            <graphic filename="../figD09/D09125.webp" type="webp" scalefit="1" scalefitwidth="248px" box="no"/>
            <caption>VGT control valve</caption>
            <calloutgroup>
                <callout1 type="arabic">VGT control valve connection</callout1>
                <callout1 type="arabic">VGT control valve</callout1>
                <callout1 type="arabic">VGT control valve connector</callout1>
                <callout1 type="arabic">VGT control valve bracket</callout1>
            </calloutgroup>
        </figure>
    </svcproc>
